  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK895">
<l>yāṇṭucceṉ ṟiyāṇṭu muḷarākār ventuppiṉ </l>
<l>vēntu ceṟappaṭ ṭavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who have incurred the wrath of a cruel and mighty potentate will not prosper wherever they may go.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
